Koeman also responded on Wednesday to Paris Saint-Germain sporting director Leonardo claiming Messi was on their wish list, by saying he would be interested in PSG's Neymar and Kylian Mbappe tooMessi saw red after swinging an arm at Bilbao's Asier Villalibre towards the end of extra-time, just before Barca went down 3-2 in SevilleThe 33-year-old is now due to miss the trip to Cornella in the Copa del Rey on Thursday and Sunday's La Liga game away to Elche, but Barca have submitted an appeal